{"tid":950000,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如果有女仔醉左主動錫你","createTime":"2018-12-21T07:54:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T23:29:01.000Z","uid":204734,"like":6,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"118a4eae0bcc26ee26313edc31e8faeee3f25107","tid":950000,"uid":204734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T07:54:16.000Z","msg":"你會有咩感覺？覺得佢係醉左亂錫 定係對你有意思？見番佢又會唔會提起？如果發現佢係對你有意思 你又會唔會追佢？<br />\n<br />\n有個女仔幾得意 但唔係好熟 <br />\n有次成班一齊飲酒 佢飲到超醉<br />\n之後冇啦啦攬實我錫我 我推開左佢 因為嚇親<br />\n明明大家都冇乜點講過野 但feel到佢平時對住我係特別怕羞<br />\n我連佢電話都冇 但又覺得佢幾qq<br />\n咁我應唔應該試下同佢發展<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋想問下如果有女仔醉左主動錫你 你會唔會推開？"},{"pid":"939de18e65a2c3feeec54a8569934e7de92926ac","tid":950000,"uid":107364,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T07:55:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c1f53f7dce5561c0ad4c1f9df0c0e94357cc3b41","tid":950000,"uid":1249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T07:55:12.000Z","msg":"#metoo"},{"pid":"b2a846de18787a4d71edf0e3bbcf3c7807d413e4","tid":950000,"uid":62550,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T07:59:37.000Z","msg":"除非樣衰 照計唔會推開"},{"pid":"ba21979cadf79b82311562677d2759073ba4115c","tid":950000,"uid":204734,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b2a846de18787a4d71edf0e3bbcf3c7807d413e4","tid":950000,"uid":62550,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T07:59:37.000Z","msg":"除非樣衰 照計唔會推開"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:01:28.000Z","msg":"姐係普通樣又冇feel 都會錫左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"426abe070c20bd80797c3d9810a71ace17ab93fc","tid":950000,"uid":5077,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:02:03.000Z","msg":"覺得佢好無禮好無規矩<br />\n會認為此女十分隨便"},{"pid":"924fb7d654cbb9cccd738c59480901610afc893e","tid":950000,"uid":227170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:02:46.000Z","msg":"如果佢記得你推開佢<br />\n你就準備比人METOO<img src=\"/assets